Package binaryTree

Interface BTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<? super T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of value stored in the tree.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinaryTree
    public interface BTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<? super T>>
    A minimum interface for sorted binary trees.
    Version:
    December 2019.
    Author:
    Hugh Osborne.
